data.description: Welcome to this charming, energy efficient home in the coveted Copper Sunrise subdivision. This well-maintained home boasts elegant granite countertops in the kitchen, adding a touch of sophistication to your culinary experience. You'll love the relaxation and serenity provided by the spa, and rejuvenating sauna, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Additionally, ample storage space ensures that your belongings are neatly organized. What sets this home apart is the eco-conscious addition of solar panels, offering energy efficiency and cost savings. With only one owner, this house exemplifies pride of ownership, making it a unique opportunity in today's market.
